                        </imageobject>
                        <caption>Options window for export a Stitch Legend</caption>
                    </mediaobject>
                </screenshot>
            </sect3>
            <sect3><title>Color Legends</title>
                <para>When you export a color legend you can update how you want the legend to look right before you save it as a file. However if you have settings that you want on at all times you can make them default by setting them in the <link linkend="options-legends-color">Options/Preferences</link>.</para>
